attachments.displayName:
POWER is useless without Great Perception....☆

For perception begets those who earnt the POWERS!*

In this life- Such is the Endorsements for-

Those who sustained; Extraordinary Richness...
Extraordinary Happiness...
Extraordinary Peace...
Extraordinary Mercy...
Extraordinary Admiration...

Experienced... At the Expense of;

Extraordinary Cruelty...

Extraordinary Affliction...

Extraordinary Depravity...

Extraordinary Solitude...

Extraordinary Burden...

Extraordinary punishment...

Extraordinary Sorrow...

Extraordinarily Pain...

Extraordinary Hurt...

Such is the gift of the Competence bestowed upon...

That they are called upon to serve the WORLD... & Acknowledged...

K.Aliy 2006

☆☆☆☆☆
